{"tid":1653155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HKmap.live即時地圖App極速被下架　蘋果：危害執法人員及港人","createTime":"2019-10-14T03:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:36:50.000Z","uid":116823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f865009f3cde850dc5ba6594d561e9c795fbdf8","tid":1653155,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"「HKmap.live即時地圖」在蘋果（apple）App Store上架僅僅兩天，便被下架，原因是該應用程式「危害到執法人員和香港居民（endanger law enforcement and residents）」。<br />\nAndoid版暫無問題，可繼續下載及使用，已下載的iPhone用戶則仍可使用；網頁版運作如常。<br />\n<br />\n香港近日不斷發生大型公眾活動，而且不時出現一些意料之外情況，有人就製作了這款名為「HKmap.live即時地圖」，讓大家可以實時匯報各區交通及突發事件，方便香港人安排行程。<br />\n<br />\n不過「HKmap.live即時地圖」開發者今早（10月10日）在Twitter表示，其App被蘋果下架，蘋果則回覆稱，「我們了解到，你的應用程序（「HKmap.live即時地圖」）的使用方式已危害到執法人員和香港居民」。<br />\n<br />\n以下為英文全文：<br />\nWe created the App Store to be a safe and trusted place to discover apps. We have learned that your app has been used in ways that endanger law enforcement and residents in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n其實「HKmap.live即時地圖」之前申請在App Store上架時已波折重重，幾經周旋才於前日（10月8日）上架。<br />\n<br />\n惟由於該App有顯示警察等行蹤，上架後引來中國內地批評。其中官媒《人民日報》昨日（10月9日）點名批評蘋果為「暴徒」護航，質問「居心何在」及「想清楚了嗎」；中國外交部亦說「任何有良知和正義感的人，都應該對示威者的暴力行為予以抵制和反對，而不是支持和縱容」。<br />\n<br />\n未知今次蘋果極速下架「HKmap.live即時地圖」，是否與前一天中國官方發聲有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/384298/hkmap-live%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96app%E6%A5%B5%E9%80%9F%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F384298%2Fhkmap-live%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596app%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259E%25B6-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C-%25E5%258D%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=5a938c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/384298/hkmap-live%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96app%E6%A5%B5%E9%80%9F%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA</a>"},{"pid":"3962b609b90685019970a94be57ba11f5e9247b8","tid":1653155,"uid":1781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysvaKG8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysvaKG8.png&h=bb885734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仆街Apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4435497125d127ea41f512afcdf8d6bfb46fd668","tid":1653155,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"你估我放個追蹤器係狗車咩<br />\n咁大部狗車閃閃下係人都見到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90cb846c05040229b3959e9854698a4e572c8b1","tid":1653155,"uid":258068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"[前線][文宣入]用黑警借車反咬政府一口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地有能力反分化政府！</span></span><br />\n推呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass